					<description><![CDATA[The thing that people need to remember is that when you want to make money with your writing, writing becomes a job. That means that you don&#039;t get to write only when you feel the urge to write. You need to write consistently on a daily basis just like you would go to work and do any other job.]]></description>
			<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>The thing that people need to remember is that when you want to make money with your writing, writing becomes a job. That means that you don&#8217;t get to write only when you feel the urge to write. You need to write consistently on a daily basis just like you would go to work and do any other job.</p>
]]></content:encoded>
		
